name: Abstractor
description:
How to use

It is recommended to write the following tokens: statue, dark, red background, hyper detailed, neon lights, cgi, gothic, glow, nether, glowing digital runes, complex details, raw, hdr, professional photo, amber and chaos, 8k detail, gilded black, glitchcore.

Copy the prompt and parameters from the preview to this model — you will not lose.

What the model is suitable for

This model creates hyper-realistic renderings and photographs in neon tones and unusual combinations of materials, colors and light-shadows.

LoRA was trained on a variety of examples, so try combinations and share your creativity in the comments.

I trained LoRA on the Deliberate_v2 model, so it's better to work with her in pairs.

Generation at high resolutions is possible.

Which model works best with

It is best to use the Deliberate_v2 model, but you can combine this LoRA with other solutions focused on photorealism, model will work perfectly with them.

Links to my resources

You will find help in my telegram chat.
My Telegram channel.
